query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS agentConfigurations (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  companyId INT NOT NULL,
  agentType ENUM('prospect', 'closer', 'solve', 'logic', 'talent', 'insight') NOT NULL,
  temperature INT DEFAULT 70 NOT NULL,
  maxTokens INT DEFAULT 2000 NOT NULL,
  systemPrompt TEXT,
  customInstructions TEXT,
  isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_company_agent (companyId, agentType)
)
